{
  "stem": "1530.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were terribly worried about me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's why I think my little sister would have never survived, because I hardly survived, and she was five years younger than I was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I still feel that that I killed her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Counted you, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, from then on, we figured it out that we should hide from every zahlappell, the five of us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we somehow managed to do this for months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, when we heard that they're coming, we-- went-- it was a very big place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'd go into the washroom, or we'd hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just running like maniacs because we didn't want to see one of us taken away or two of us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister Chicha--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Berta.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, Isabelle got the job in a place called [GERMAN]--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, in our block, where they selected all the clothes that we brought in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because of that, she got one piece of bread-- which wasn't bread, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was sawdust.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was more than not having it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then she got some kind of little typhoid, and we had to take care of her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she pushed Chicha into her job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Chicha came home one night with a knife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was like having everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't have to break your bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could, for five people, cut very thin pieces and-- and, you know, divide it equally.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one soup, once a day, maybe in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was like-- how do you say, a big sty, what they give for pigs?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Slop.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It looked like slop.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think-- I don't know whether they were prisoners, or Germans came with a truck or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were always screaming about everything, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
